ed="J" n="0656b01"/><anchor n="J.26.B186.0656b01"/><head>天童<persName key="A012053">林野奇</persName>和尚行狀</head><p xml:id="pJ26p0656b0101">……<lb
ed="J" n="0656b22"/>至庚午春聞<persName key="A003688">悟</persName>過當湖，遣護關者求開示。<persName key="A003688">悟</persName>云：「教<ref type="person" target="#A012053">他</ref><lb
ed="J" n="0656b23"/>關中莫妄想。」……<lb
ed="J" n="0657a01"/>……未幾<persName key="A003688">悟</persName>因事出山，<ref type="person" target="#A012053">師</ref>隨至嘉禾，寓<persName key="A037498">黃闇齋</persName>觀<lb
ed="J" n="0657a02"/>察素園中受付囑焉！……<lb
ed="J" n="0657a04"/>……<persName key="A004667">顧<lb
ed="J" n="0657a05"/>瑞屏</persName>宗伯同寧紹兩郡當道縉紳，再三敦請，<persName key="A003688">悟</persName>和尚<lb
ed="J" n="0657a06"/>復返天童。冬期立<ref type="person" target="#A012053">師</ref>為西堂。……<lb
ed="J" n="0657a10"/>……<persName key="A042720">孫<lb
ed="J" n="0657a11"/><roleName>司馬</roleName>碩膚</persName>諸檀護堅請開法，風雨晦明歷諸艱。……<lb
ed="J" n="0657a14"/>……平素書問<lb
ed="J" n="0657a15"/>訶禁，弢藏天台。惟<persName key="A042721">陳木叔</persName>司馬為所雅重，乙酉春有<lb
ed="J" n="0657a16"/>詩贈「嶺外遊雲來又去，忘年拙衲定荒嶺」之句。丙戌<lb
ed="J" n="0657a17"/>秋<persName key="A042721">陳</persName>以絕命詩十二章，手書告別<ref type="person" target="#A012053">師</ref>。……<lb
ed="J" n="0657a21"/>……丁亥冬至嘉<lb
ed="J" n="0657a22"/>禾黃觀察闇齋、<persName key="A001004">高<roleName>水部</roleName>寓公</persName>、汪進士曾城諸縉紳檀<lb
ed="J" n="0657a23"/>護請住東塔寺安期，旋為<persName key="A042722">錢<roleName>閣學</roleName>塞菴</persName>公暨諸緇白<lb
ed="J" n="0657a24"/>請住棲真古剎。……<lb
ed="J" n="0657b15"/>……<persName key="A014742">雪竇</persName>和尚問病而<lb
ed="J" n="0657b16"/>至，必欲<ref type="person" target="#A012053">師</ref>歸方丈。<ref type="person" target="#A012053">師</ref>從容而返。築塔無基，堪輿擬以<lb
ed="J" n="0657b17"/>新菴定穴。<ref type="person" target="#A012053">師</ref>聞之，斷不許可。……</p>
